== Events == * [[Kaika Tennō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|157 BC|ja|紀元前157|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The 9th Emperor, {{ill|Kaika Tennō|ja|開化天皇|12=draft|12=draft}}, ascended to the throne.{{要出典|date=2021-03}} * [[Kenkō (era)|Kenkō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|316|ja|316|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Western Jin Dynasty collapsed. * [[Genroku]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1688|ja|1688|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunayoshi|ja|徳川綱吉|12=draft|12=draft}} selected his aide, {{ill|Yanagisawa Yoshiyasu|ja|柳沢吉保|12=draft|12=draft}}, as his official (sōi) and advisor. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Five of Japan’s first female exchange students, including {{ill|Tsuda Umeko|ja|津田梅子|12=draft|12=draft}}, departed Yokohama for the United States. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – A governmental edict abolished traditional formal attire (such as the kabuto and hakama) in favor of Western dress.
== Births == * [[Chishō]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1178|ja|1178|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Antoku Tennō|ja|安徳天皇|1=Emperor Antoku|2=ja|3=安徳天皇|4=de|5=Antoku|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 81st Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1185|ja|1185|12=draft|12=draft}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|安徳天皇}}</ref>
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kunishi Chisanao|ja|国司親相|12=draft|12=draft}}, a senior retainer (家老) of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1842|ja|1842|12=draft|12=draft}}). * In the same Genji 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} 1864, December 10) – {{ill|Fukuhara Motomi|ja|福原元僴|12=draft|12=draft}}, another senior retainer of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1815|ja|1815|12=draft|12=draft}}).
== Commemorations ==
