== Deaths == * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kunishi Chisanao|ja|国司親相|qq=}}, a senior retainer (家老) of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1842|ja|1842|qq=}}). * In the same Genji 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} 1864, December 10) – {{ill|Fukuhara Motomi|ja|福原元僴|qq=}}, another senior retainer of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1815|ja|1815|qq=}}).
