{{Lunisolar November|qq=}}
'''November 12''' is the 12th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* [[Kaika Tennō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|157 BC|ja|紀元前157|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The 9th Emperor, {{ill|Kaika Tennō|ja|開化天皇|qq=|12=draft}}, ascended to the throne.{{要出典|date=2021-03|qq=}}
* [[Kenkō (era)|Kenkō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|316|ja|316|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Western Jin Dynasty collapsed.
* [[Genroku]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1688|ja|1688|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunayoshi|ja|徳川綱吉|qq=|12=draft}} selected his aide, {{ill|Yanagisawa Yoshiyasu|ja|柳沢吉保|qq=|12=draft}}, as his official (sōi) and advisor.
* [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=|12=draft}}) – Five of Japan’s first female exchange students, including {{ill|Tsuda Umeko|ja|津田梅子|qq=|12=draft}}, departed Yokohama for the United States.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|12=draft}}) – A governmental edict abolished traditional formal attire (such as the kabuto and hakama) in favor of Western dress.

== Births ==
* [[Chishō]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1178|ja|1178|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Antoku Tennō|ja|安徳天皇|1=Emperor Antoku|2=ja|3=安徳天皇|4=de|5=Antoku|qq=|12=draft}}, the 81st Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1185|ja|1185|qq=|12=draft}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|安徳天皇|qq=}}</ref>

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kunishi Chisanao|ja|国司親相|qq=|12=draft}}, a senior retainer (家老) of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1842|ja|1842|qq=|12=draft}}).
* In the same Genji 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} 1864, December 10) – {{ill|Fukuhara Motomi|ja|福原元僴|qq=|12=draft}}, another senior retainer of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1815|ja|1815|qq=|12=draft}}).

