{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月十二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 12일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 12''' is the 12th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft}}.
== Events == * [[Kaika Tennō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|157 BC|ja|紀元前157|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The 9th Emperor, {{ill|Kaika Tennō|ja|開化天皇|qq=|qq=draft}}, ascended to the throne.{{要出典|date=2021-03|qq=}} * [[Kenkō (era)|Kenkō]] 4th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|316|ja|316|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The Western Jin Dynasty collapsed. * [[Genroku]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1688|ja|1688|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunayoshi|ja|徳川綱吉|qq=|qq=draft}} selected his aide, {{ill|Yanagisawa Yoshiyasu|ja|柳沢吉保|qq=|qq=draft}}, as his official (sōi) and advisor. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – Five of Japan’s first female exchange students, including {{ill|Tsuda Umeko|ja|津田梅子|qq=|qq=draft}}, departed Yokohama for the United States. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – A governmental edict abolished traditional formal attire (such as the kabuto and hakama) in favor of Western dress.
== Births == * [[Chishō]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1178|ja|1178|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Antoku Tennō|ja|安徳天皇|1=Emperor Antoku|2=ja|3=安徳天皇|4=de|5=Antoku|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 81st Emperor of Japan (died {{ill|1185|ja|1185|qq=|qq=draft}}).<ref>{{Kotobank|安徳天皇|qq=}}</ref>
== Deaths == * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1864|ja|1864|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 10|ja|12月10日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kunishi Chisanao|ja|国司親相|qq=|qq=draft}}, a senior retainer (家老) of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1842|ja|1842|qq=|qq=draft}}). * In the same Genji 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} 1864, December 10) – {{ill|Fukuhara Motomi|ja|福原元僴|qq=|qq=draft}}, another senior retainer of the Chōshū Domain (born {{ill|1815|ja|1815|qq=|qq=draft}}).
